org.enterprisedomain.classmaker

Interface Contribution

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.core.runtime.IAdapterFactory, org.eclipse.core.runtime.jobs.ISchedulingRule, Item, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, Project
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ContributionImpl

    public interface Contribution
extends Project, Item, org.eclipse.core.runtime.IAdapterFactory
    A representation of the model object 'Contribution'. Software contribution project item. Basically, it contibutes the software piece to the body of main program.

    The following features are supported:

    • Dependencies
    • Revision
    • Revisions
    • State
    • Latest Version
    • Model Resource Adapter
    See Also:
    ClassMakerPackage.getContribution()
